      <b>
        "The Baron's daughter is missing, and you are the man to find her. No problem.
        With your inexhaustible arsenal of hard-boiled similes, there is nothing you can't handle."
      </b>
    </p>
    <p>
      In PataNoir, you solve crime by manipulating the hard-boiled metaphors used by the main character
      to make sense of the world in which he lives.
    </p>
    <p>
      @*<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/patanoir/id987561337"><img src="../Images/itunes.png" border="0" alt="iTunes" width="110" height="40"></a>*@
