<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Trapped in Time</h2>
        <p><img src="../Images/Watch.jpg" alt="Watch" width="175" height="175"></p>
        <p><b>"A Science Fiction adventure where YOU are the hero!"</b></p>
        <p>Old-school choose-your-own-adventure in PDF format. Can you succesfully complete your trip through time?</p>
        <p>
            <a href="http://ifdb.tads.org/viewgame?id=juj5b61griyoswn2"><img src="../Images/ifdb.png" border="0" alt="IFDB" width="110" height="40"></a>
