        <h2>Internal Vigilance</h2>
        <p><img src="../Images/Agent.png" alt="Internal Vigilance" width="175" height="175"></p>
        <p>
            <b>
                "You are informed that a new prisoner was brought in recently. Your job, as
                usual, is to interrogate him and determine whether he poses a threat to The Union.
                This should not be a problem. You are a trained interrogator."
            </b>
        </p>
        <p>
            The first game ever produced by SiChris Productions, "Internal Vigilance" has some
            rough edges, but still provides an entertaining and thought-provoking experience.
